{"tid":520945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【殖民法庭】梁愛詩：若一地兩檢決定遇司法覆核　法院或提請釋法","createTime":"2018-01-06T03:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T03:14:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f7436ef86a3e1b16c5ac3df5381579e7763204bf","tid":520945,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1373683_1_20180106104012.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1373683_1_20180106104012.jpg&h=b979ba9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會副主任梁愛詩表示，香港法院沒有權就人大常委會的決定行使「違憲審查權」。如果日後有市民就人大常委會對高鐵「一地兩檢」的決定提出司法覆核，她估計到時終審法院很大可能會提請人大釋法，相信人大常委會到時也不會改變有關決定。<br />\n<br />\n梁愛詩出席電台節目時又說，不認為人大常委會需要借助關於「一地兩檢」的決定，尋找缺口為《基本法》23條立法鋪路。"},{"pid":"4c04aa09c95630bce8922c1f55a10fe5f42515f9","tid":520945,"uid":88123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T03:37:10.000Z","msg":"日日咒呢條八婆死"},{"pid":"6e097f11d647451669dc06aecbf725287a318fd5","tid":520945,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}